org.gearvrf

Interface GVRAndroidResource.Callback<T extends GVRHybridObject>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    GVRAndroidResource.BitmapTextureCallback, GVRAndroidResource.CancelableCallback<T>, GVRAndroidResource.CompressedTextureCallback, GVRAndroidResource.MeshCallback, GVRAndroidResource.TextureCallback
    Enclosing class:
    GVRAndroidResource

    public static interface GVRAndroidResource.Callback<T extends GVRHybridObject>
    Callback interface for asynchronous resource loading. None of the asynchronous resource [textures, and meshes] loading methods that take a GVRAndroidResource parameter return a value. You must supply a copy of this interface to get results.

    While you will often create a callback for each load request, the APIs do each include the GVRAndroidResource that you are loading. This lets you use the same callback implementation with multiple resources.
